<br>
I watched the ooc discussions this morning and then read this post and I have a few objective considerations I would like to share.<br>
<br>
1) CiH was quite clear that they would not respect this list, so I find it not worth the time to express anger and frustration at their taking this spawn.<br>
<br>
2) The pervasive attitude of CiH posters of &quot;we're gonna do whatever we want as long as it's not against the rules&quot; seems to offend some of the Drinal community, myself included. Why? Well it's pretty simple, just cause something is not against the rules does not mean it is moral.  <br>
<br>
3) Those that are upset and complaining need to get organized if they hope to teach CiH to play by the &quot;civilized&quot; rules being presented by the drinal community.  VI may make the rules we are forced to play by in game, however as a community we also make some of our own rules. VI does not respect camps in the game, however the community supports the idea of camps, and people are pressured to observe them for the most part. CiH members support and observe this unwritten rule, so they obviously will support an unwritten rule when it is to their benefit.<br>
<br>
4) The idea that ALL members of a guild should not be held accountable and responsible for a guild action is ridiculous.  As long as you deny that those you know in a guild are responsible for supporting the actions of said guild, it will not be possible to instigate change.<br>
<br>
So I guess with those things said, grats Ndaani on your epic, and CiH on your kill.  My sympathies Reeko not getting the reward on your efforts.  I would like to conclude this post with a plea:<br>
<br>
Please if you want to change the way that this is working, take action.  Start a movement to blackball guilds that will not support the Ragefire list if you want it to be supported by the whole server. Do not accept that some people may say they won't agree to play nice with the rest of us in a mutually agreeable fashion. Many of the people on this list have friends in the CiH (or any other guilds not agreeing to said list) pressure those friends, pressure friends that have friends in the guild. Stop the complaining and do something about this.<br>
<br>
Phaestus Aesthete<br>
57 Enchanter<br>
